# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:3
translate spanish work1_a661a5bb:

    # "Work goes fairly normally for the first three hours, then when it's nearly time to go, Mrs. Mills comes up to me."
    "El trabajo transcurre con bastante normalidad durante las primeras tres horas, y luego, cuando ya casi es hora de irse, la Sra. Mills se me acerca."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:6
translate spanish work1_05636015:

    # "She stands close and puts a hand on my shoulder."
    "Se queda cerca de mí y me pone una mano en el hombro."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:7
translate spanish work1_c5e6ce57:

    # bs "You've done good work. I'm glad I decided to hire you, even though you seemed a little dense at first."
    bs "Has hecho un buen trabajo. Me alegro de haber decidido contratarte, aunque al principio parecías un poco torpe."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:8
translate spanish work1_d4d85540:

    # bs "I hope you'll stick around, because this week has been good."
    bs "Espero que te quedes, porque esta semana ha ido bien."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:10
translate spanish work1_208ce8ca:

    # bs "Here's your paycheck for the week."
    bs "Aquí tienes tu nómina de esta semana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:11
translate spanish work1_f9dc9fe0:

    # "She hands me a paycheck for $300."
    "Me entrega un cheque por valor de 300 dólares."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:13
translate spanish work1_63dc4511:

    # bs "After this check, the rest will be deposited directly to your bank account."
    bs "A partir de ahora, el resto se te ingresará directamente en tu cuenta bancaria."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:14
translate spanish work1_95914f27:

    # bs "Have a good weekend and I'll see you on Monday."
    bs "Que pases un buen fin de semana y nos vemos el lunes."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:15
translate spanish work1_bd884b3c:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am, thank you."
    pc "Sí, señora, gracias."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:16
translate spanish work1_6e413467:

    # "I take the paycheck and leave. This money will definitely come in handy. There's plenty of things that I need, and Lisa could always use some help around the house."
    "Cojo el cheque y me voy. Este dinero me vendrá muy bien. Hay muchas cosas que necesito, y a Lisa siempre le viene bien un poco de ayuda en casa."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:19
translate spanish work1_cf3bc495:

    # "I tell Dana goodnight as I pass and head outside."
    "Le doy las buenas noches a Dana al pasar y salgo."

